@startuml
actor UserA
participant "Client App" as App
participant "Server Gate" as SRV
database "Database" as DB
actor UserB

UserA -> App: Введення тексту + Click Send
App -> App: Шифрування (MTProto)
App -> SRV: POST /sendMessage
activate SRV
SRV -> DB: Save Message
SRV --> App: ACK (Message ID, Status 200)
deactivate SRV
SRV -> UserB: Push Notification / WebSocket Update
@enduml